onyx-127vm14: bash: line 1: 2522554 Aborted                 (core dumped) LUSTRE=&quot;/usr/lib64/lustre&quot; sh -c &quot;/usr/sbin/lctl set_param -P -d osc.*.max_pages_per_rpc&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
